{"title":"Java学习-HelloWorld!","date":"2018-03-11T00:20:25.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Mar 11, 2018","L":"03/11/2018","MM-DD":"03-11"},"link":"Learning/a0fc4dd9990c","tags":["Java"],"categories":["Learning"],"updated":"2021-02-27T13:47:38.633Z","content":"<p><strong>这学期学习Java，我就用博客记录一下我整个学习的内容吧。</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Java从main方法开始执行</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">DemoClass</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">(String\\[\\] args)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">//Java程序从这里开始执行//表示本行是注释</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    System.out.println(<span class=\"string\">&quot;Hello,World!&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    System.out.println(<span class=\"string\">&quot;世界,你好!&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    System.out.println(<span class=\"string\">&quot;大家好!&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>执行上面的程序会输出:</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Hello,World!</span><br><span class=\"line\">世界,你好!</span><br><span class=\"line\">大家好!</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol>\n<li>Java文件的名字必须是public class 后面的名字(通常称为类名).java 例如上面的程序必须放在DemoClass.java文件中.</li>\n<li>英文字符大小写必须一致. Java认为大写和小写的字符不是同一个字符.</li>\n<li>Java语言中用{}表示范围.\n<ul>\n<li>类名后面的一对{}表示这个类的包含的范围. void main(String[] args)后面的一对{}表示这个方法的包含的范围.</li>\n<li>方法名字后面的一对()是方法要处理的变量.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>分号表示一条语句的结尾. 双引号”“表示字符串的开始和结尾.</li>\n<li>英文的句号(.)可以读作”的”, 用于限定范围. 例如语句System.out.println(“Hello,World!”);其真实含义是计算机系统(System)的标准输出(out,显示器)的输出一行方法(println)负责处理字符串”Hello,World!”, 也就是在计算机的显示器上打印(显示)一行文字Hello,World!.</li>\n<li>Java的源程序文件通常用包(package)组织起来， 包名就是目录名。</li>\n</ol>\n","prev":{"title":"Java学习-Java基本输入输出","link":"Learning/e622c9e836e9"},"next":{"title":"修改WordPress主题字体，使用自定义TTF字体","link":"Learning/f0c1e4e6fd81"},"plink":"https://www.zzboy.cn/Learning/a0fc4dd9990c/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Patrick Jun","link":"<a href=\"https://www.zzboy.cn/Learning/a0fc4dd9990c/\" title=\"Java学习-HelloWorld!\">https://www.zzboy.cn/Learning/a0fc4dd9990c/</a>","license":"自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名 (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"March 11, 2018"}}